  "body": "<!---\r\nThanks for creating a Pull Request 💖!\r\n\r\nPlease read the following before submitting:\r\n- PRs that adds new external dependencies might take a while to review.\r\n- Keep your PR as small as possible.\r\n- Limit your PR to one type (docs, feature, refactoring, ci, or bugfix)\r\n-->\r\n\r\nCloses # <!-- Github issue # here -->\r\n\r\n## 📝 Description\r\n\r\nExport \"useEditableContext\" to enable extension of Editable component\r\n\r\n## ⛳️ Current behavior (updates)\r\n\r\nCannot access the Editable context therefore customising the behavior of editable is very challenging.\r\n\r\n## 🚀 New behavior\r\n\r\nCan import \"useEditableContext\" hook therefore can create custom Editable components more easily. For example, the editable component can be extended to support a wide range of datatypes, not just text or textarea.\r\n\r\n## 💣 Is this a breaking change (Yes/No):\r\n\r\nNo\r\n\r\n## 📝 Additional Information\r\n\r\n",
